{"by":"thesmok","id":47775715,"parent":47764215,"text":"As a citizen of a country currently defending in a war, unmanned systems are a literal lifesaver. We can send an armed robot where we previously would have to send a soldier. This is a good thing and before the war many had the same pacifist sentiment in the tech sector, but it&#x27;s completely reversed now.<p>Though I can understand your position being in a country that&#x27;s not defending itself currently.","time":1776237501,"type":"comment"}